{"id":975,"date":"2020-08-14T17:14:50","date_gmt":"2020-08-14T10:14:50","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/?page_id=975"},"modified":"2024-04-12T15:02:29","modified_gmt":"2024-04-12T08:02:29","slug":"green-policy","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/green-policy\/","title":{"rendered":"Green Policy"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-47eu0ati fg-image  img-responsive full-width hidden-xs fg-text-dark\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Header-Going-Green-Caravelle.jpg 1360w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/d9bbc0ffc3b6597b323500d87ecabcb9_Header-Going-Green-Caravelle-320-c-100.jpg 320w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/d9bbc0ffc3b6597b323500d87ecabcb9_Header-Going-Green-Caravelle-768-c-100.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/d9bbc0ffc3b6597b323500d87ecabcb9_Header-Going-Green-Caravelle-992-c-100.jpg 992w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/d9bbc0ffc3b6597b323500d87ecabcb9_Header-Going-Green-Caravelle-1200-c-100.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1360px) 100vw, 1360px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Header-Going-Green-Caravelle.jpg\" alt=\"Header-Going-Green-Caravelle\"><style><\/style><script type=\"text\/javascript\"><\/script><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-4bk31trt fg-image  img-responsive full-width hidden-sm hidden-md hidden-lg fg-text-dark\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/d9bbc0ffc3b6597b323500d87ecabcb9_Header-Going-Green-Caravelle-1360-765-c-90.jpg 1360w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/72a050e78b696861da139be09a39abc9_d9bbc0ffc3b6597b323500d87ecabcb9_Header-Going-Green-Caravelle-1360-765-c-90-320-c-100.jpg 320w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/72a050e78b696861da139be09a39abc9_d9bbc0ffc3b6597b323500d87ecabcb9_Header-Going-Green-Caravelle-1360-765-c-90-768-c-100.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/72a050e78b696861da139be09a39abc9_d9bbc0ffc3b6597b323500d87ecabcb9_Header-Going-Green-Caravelle-1360-765-c-90-992-c-100.jpg 992w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/72a050e78b696861da139be09a39abc9_d9bbc0ffc3b6597b323500d87ecabcb9_Header-Going-Green-Caravelle-1360-765-c-90-1200-c-100.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1360px) 100vw, 1360px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/d9bbc0ffc3b6597b323500d87ecabcb9_Header-Going-Green-Caravelle-1360-765-c-90.jpg\" alt=\"Header-Going-Green-Caravelle\" id=\"Image mobile\"><style><\/style><script type=\"text\/javascript\"><\/script><section class=\"ffb-id-47ovocvo fg-section fg-text-dark\" id=\"intro\"><div class=\"fg-container container-fluid fg-container-fluid fg-container-lvl--1 fg-container-no-padding\"><div class=\"fg-row row fg-row-no-gutter   \" ><div class=\"ffb-id-47ovocvp fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><h1 class=\"ffb-id-47ovocvu fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p>CARAVELLE SAIGON ENVIRONMENTAL, ENERGY &amp; SOCIAL SUSTAINABILITY POLICY<\/p>\n<p><\/h1><div class=\"ffb-id-47ovocvv fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">As raising the awareness in being environmentally friendly, effecient energy use, and sustainable development, as well as our desire in contributing to the local community, Caravelle Saigon commits in being ecofriendly, thus continually develop and follow our sustainable development policy in Environment, Energy, and Society.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">With the stunning view to the Opera House and only a few minutes&rsquo; walk to culture heritages and shopping center, Caravelle Saigon is honoured to be the icon of Ho Chi Minh city, proudly stand strong throughout years of history. Caravelle Saigon offers 5-star accommodation services with 333 modern luxurious rooms, along with multi-functional banquet rooms, pool, fitness &amp; spa services, restaurants and bars.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">At Caravelle, we prioritize and secure a safe, ecofriendly workplace for our associates, while encouraging green initiatives to lighten the impact towards the environment. With the mission, we had established, implemented, and maintained our Environmental Management System and Energy Management System following EarthCheck standards.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">CARAVELLE SAIGON COMMITTED TO:<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Avoid<\/strong> negative impact on environment.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Minimize<\/strong> usage and maximize effectiveness of natural resources.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Continuously<\/strong> improvement to ensure the effectiveness of green initiatives<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Compliance<\/strong> with government regulations in environmental perspectives and establish a system to annually evaluate the workplace health &amp; safety following Earthcheck standard.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Focus<\/strong> in recruiting local labors.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Prioritize<\/strong> using local products and services, and compliance to fair trading regulations.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Enhance<\/strong> associates&rsquo; awareness in environmental &amp; social sustainability and energy efficiency.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Caravelle Saigon appreciates and encourages the green initiates from associates, customers, partners and local community; of which will be the direction for Caravelle Saigon to continually develop our sustainably programs in terms of environmental, energy, and socially. The guideline will be updated annually.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style>.ffb-id-47ovocvo{ padding-top: 50px;padding-right: 50px;padding-bottom: 50px;padding-left: 50px;} .ffb-id-47ovocvp{ text-align: center;}.ffb-id-47ovocvv ,.ffb-id-47ovocvv:before,.ffb-id-47ovocvv:after,.ffb-id-47ovocvv *,.ffb-id-47ovocvv *:before,.ffb-id-47ovocvv *:after{ color: #797979 !important;}.ffb-id-47ovocvv{ font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}.ffb-id-47ovocvv:before,.ffb-id-47ovocvv:after,.ffb-id-47ovocvv:hover,.ffb-id-47ovocvv:focus,.ffb-id-47ovocvv *,.ffb-id-47ovocvv *:before,.ffb-id-47ovocvv *:after,.ffb-id-47ovocvv *:hover,.ffb-id-47ovocvv *:focus{ font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}.ffb-id-47ovocvv{ font-size: 13px !important;}.ffb-id-47ovocvv ,.ffb-id-47ovocvv:before,.ffb-id-47ovocvv:after,.ffb-id-47ovocvv:hover,.ffb-id-47ovocvv:focus,.ffb-id-47ovocvv *,.ffb-id-47ovocvv *:before,.ffb-id-47ovocvv *:after,.ffb-id-47ovocvv *:hover,.ffb-id-47ovocvv *:focus{ font-size: 13px !important;}.ffb-id-47ovocvu ,.ffb-id-47ovocvu:before,.ffb-id-47ovocvu:after,.ffb-id-47ovocvu *,.ffb-id-47ovocvu *:before,.ffb-id-47ovocvu *:after{ color: #490042 !important;}.ffb-id-47ovocvu{ font-family: Georgia, serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}.ffb-id-47ovocvu:before,.ffb-id-47ovocvu:after,.ffb-id-47ovocvu:hover,.ffb-id-47ovocvu:focus,.ffb-id-47ovocvu *,.ffb-id-47ovocvu *:before,.ffb-id-47ovocvu *:after,.ffb-id-47ovocvu *:hover,.ffb-id-47ovocvu *:focus{ font-family: Georgia, serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}.ffb-id-47ovocvu{ font-size: 35px !important;}.ffb-id-47ovocvu ,.ffb-id-47ovocvu:before,.ffb-id-47ovocvu:after,.ffb-id-47ovocvu:hover,.ffb-id-47ovocvu:focus,.ffb-id-47ovocvu *,.ffb-id-47ovocvu *:before,.ffb-id-47ovocvu *:after,.ffb-id-47ovocvu *:hover,.ffb-id-47ovocvu *:focus{ font-size: 35px !important;}<\/style><script type=\"text\/javascript\"><\/script><section class=\"ffb-id-6hi44vpa fg-section